<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to LinkedInPulse</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .feature-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .feature-box h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .trial-badge {
            background-color: #ffeaa7;
            color: #d63031;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üéâ Welcome to LinkedInPulse!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hey <%= name %>,</h2>

            <p>Welcome aboard! We're thrilled to have you join thousands of professionals who are transforming their
                LinkedIn presence with AI-powered content.</p>

            <div class="trial-badge">
                ‚è∞ Your <%= trialDays %>-Day Free Trial Starts Now!
            </div>

            <p>During your trial, you'll have full access to:</p>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>üöÄ AI-Powered Content Generation</h3>
                <p>Create engaging LinkedIn posts in seconds with our advanced AI</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>üéØ Custom AI Personas</h3>
                <p>Train AI to write in your unique voice and style</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>üí° Viral Hook Generator</h3>
                <p>Start every post with attention-grabbing hooks</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>üìä Performance Analytics</h3>
                <p>Track your content performance and optimize strategy</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:3000' %>/dashboard" class="cta-button">
                    Start Creating Content Now ‚Üí
                </a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Quick Start Tips:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Complete your profile setup for personalized content</li>
                <li>Create your first AI persona to match your brand voice</li>
                <li>Generate your first post and see the magic happen</li>
                <li>Schedule your content strategy for the week</li>
            </ul>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Need help getting started? Reply to this email - we're here to help!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">To your LinkedIn success,<br><strong>The LinkedInPulse Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> LinkedInPulse. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>